Class BattleCharacter

java.lang.Object
  Character
      BattleCharacter
Direct Known Subclasses:
Enemy, Hero
public abstract class BattleCharacter
extends Character

Abstract class for characters that can engage in battles. Introduces health, attack power, and defense attributes.
